(this["webpackJsonppraveenoruganti-courses"]=this["webpackJsonppraveenoruganti-courses"]||[]).push([[228],{797:function(e,n,s){"use strict";s.r(n),n.default=" **How to add spring security to a spring boot application?**\n\n1. Add the below dependency in pom.xml\n\n```jsx\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>\n  <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-security</artifactId>\n</dependency>\n```\n\n2. Once i add the above spring security dependency, the security will be enabled by default.\n\nSpring generally uses Filters for providing the default security mechanism.\n\n**Spring Security default behaviour**\n\n- Adds mandatory authentication for all URL's\n- Adds login form\n- Handles login error\n- Creates a user and sets a default password\n\nNow open URL [http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students](http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students), u will see below login form\n\n![screenshot of the app](https://praveenoruganti.github.io/courses/images/springboot/formbased.PNG)\n\n**Now whats the user id and password i need to provide?**\n\nAs you have not configured user id and password, at starup of sping boot application, spring security component by default generates a password and username is **user** as shown in below screenshot.\n\n![screenshot of the app](https://praveenoruganti.github.io/courses/images/springboot/formbased1.PNG)\n\nNow lets provide the username as **user** and password as **04547a8d-b3a5-4de9-8261-6e74e8752370** and click on Sign in button.\n\nLogin is successful and it will show the service response.\n\n![screenshot of the app](https://praveenoruganti.github.io/courses/images/springboot/formbased2.PNG)\n\nNow lets set our customized user and password in application.yml\n\n![screenshot of the app](https://praveenoruganti.github.io/courses/images/springboot/formbased3.PNG)\n\nNow open [http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students](http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students) and enter userid as **praveenoruganti** and password as **springsecurity**.\n\nLogin successful and it will show the service response.\n\n![screenshot of the app](https://praveenoruganti.github.io/courses/images/springboot/formbased4.PNG)\n\n\nNow open [http://localhost:8080/logout](http://localhost:8080/logout)\n\n![screenshot of the app](https://praveenoruganti.github.io/courses/images/springboot/logout.PNG)\n\nNow click on Log Out Button\n\n![screenshot of the app](https://praveenoruganti.github.io/courses/images/springboot/logout1.PNG) "}}]);